<item>
            <title>[SOLR-865] Support document updates in binary format</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-865</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SolrJ uses the fast and compact &apos;javabin&apos; format for querying Solr which is a huge performance improvement over the xml format. We should make it possible to use the &apos;javabin&apos; format for document updates as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
