                            <comment id="12660455" author="noble.paul" created="Sat, 3 Jan 2009 09:58:14 +0000"  >&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A new UpdateHandler called BinaryUpdateRequestHandler&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A codec for UpdateRequest. The codec does streaming for unmarshalling&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;RequestWriter is pluggable for CommonsHttpSolrServer. default is xml and binary format can be used by server.setRequestWriter(new BinaryRequestWriter());&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A testcase added LargeVolumeBinaryJettyTest It fails saying  &lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:4020/example/update/javabin&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://localhost:4020/example/update/javabin&lt;/a&gt; canot be found . has to be fixed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
